<sent type="title" lang="chi" page="01a" n="1">詩經諺解 卷之三</sent>
<sent type="title3" lang="chi" page="01a" n="2">鄘風</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="01a" n="3">汎彼柏舟ᅵ여 在彼中河ᅵ로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="01a" n="3">汎 뎌 栢舟ᅵ여 뎌 中河의 잇도다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="01a" n="4">髧彼兩髦ᅵ 實維我儀니</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="01a" n="4">髧 뎌 兩髦ᅵ 진실로 내 儀니</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="01a" n="5">之死ᅵ언 矢靡他호리라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="01a" n="5">죽으매 니디언 矢호리니 他ᅵ 업소리라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="01a-01b" n="6">母也天只시니 不諒人只아</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="01a-01b" n="6">母ᅵ 天이시니 사을 諒티 아니시냐</sent><!--^시-->

<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="01b" n="1">汎彼柏舟ᅵ여 在彼河側이로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="01b" n="1">汎 뎌 栢舟ᅵ여 뎌 河ᄉ 애 잇도다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="01b" n="2">髧彼兩髦ᅵ 實維我特이니</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="01b" n="2">髧 뎌 兩髦ᅵ 진실로 내 特이니</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="01b" n="3">之死ᅵ언 矢靡慝호리라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="01b" n="3">죽으매 니디언 矢호리니 慝이 업소리라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="01b" n="4">母也天只시니 不諒人只아</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="01b" n="4">母ᅵ 天이시니 사을 諒티 아니시냐</sent>

<sent type="title4" lang="chi" page="02a" n="1">柏舟 二章</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="02a" n="2">牆有茨니 不可掃也ᅵ로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="02a" n="2">牆애 茨ᅵ 이시니 可히 埽티 몯리로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="02a" n="3">中冓之言이여 不可道也ᅵ로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="02a" n="3">中冓읫 言이여 可히 道티 몯리로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="02a" n="4">所可道也댄 言之醜也ᅵ로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="02a" n="4">可히 道 밴댄 言이 醜홉도다</sent>

<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="02b" n="1">牆有茨니 不可襄也ᅵ로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="02b" n="1">牆애 茨ᅵ 이시니 可히 襄티 몯리로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="02b" n="2">中冓之言이여 不可詳也ᅵ로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="02b" n="2">中冓읫 言이여 可히 詳티 몯리로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="02b" n="3">所可詳也댄 言之長也ᅵ로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="02b" n="3">可히 詳 밴댄 言이 長도다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="02b" n="4">牆有茨니 不可束也ᅵ로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="02b" n="4">牆애 茨ᅵ 이시니 可히 束디 몯리로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="02b-03a" n="5">中冓之言이여 不可讀也ᅵ로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="02b-03a" n="5">中冓읫 言이여 可히 讀디 몯리로다</sent><!--몯^-->

<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="03a" n="1">所可讀也댄 言之辱也ᅵ로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="03a" n="1">可히 讀 밴댄 言이 辱홉도다</sent>
<sent type="title4" lang="chi" page="03a" n="2">牆有茨 三章</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="03a" n="3">君子偕老ᅵ라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="03a" n="3">君子와  늘글디라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="03a" n="4">副笄六珈ᅵ니</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="03a" n="4">副고 笄 여 고대 珈여시니</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="03a" n="5">委委佗佗ᅵ며 如山如河ᅵ라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="03a" n="5">委委며 佗佗며 山 며 河 디라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="03a-03b" n="6">象服是宜어 子之不淑은 云如之何오</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="03a-03b" n="6">象服이 이 宜거 子의 淑디 아니홈은 엇디리오</sent><!--영인본상 ‘아니홈’의 ‘아니’는 ‘아나’와 같이 보이기도 함--><!--象^服-->

<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="03b" n="1">玼兮玼兮니 其之翟也ᅵ로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="03b" n="1">玼며 玼니 그의 翟이로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="03b" n="2">鬒髮如雲니 不屑髢也ᅵ로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="03b" n="2">鬒 髮이 雲 니 髢 屑티 아니놋다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="03b-04a" n="3">玉之瑱也ᅵ며 象之揥也ᅵ며 揚且之晳也ᅵ로소니</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="03b-04a" n="3">玉으로  瑼이며 象으로  揥며 揚고 晳도소니</sent><!--며 ^ 揚-->

<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="04a" n="1">胡然而天也ᅵ며 胡然而帝也오</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="04a" n="1">엇더 天이며 엇더 帝오</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="04a" n="2">瑳兮瑳兮니 其之展也ᅵ로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="04a" n="2">瑳며 瑳니 그의 展이로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="04a" n="3">蒙彼縐絺니 是紲袢也ᅵ로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="04a" n="3">뎌 縐絺예 蒙니 이 紲絆엿도다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="04a-04b" n="4">子之淸揚이여 揚且之顔也ᅵ로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="04a-04b" n="4">子의 淸고 揚홈이여 揚고 顔도다</sent><!--도^다-->

<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="04b" n="1">展如之人兮여 邦之媛也ᅵ로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="04b" n="1">진실로 이러  사이여 邦읫 媛이로다</sent>
<sent type="title4" lang="chi" page="04b" n="2">君子偕老 三章</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="04b" n="3">爰采唐矣 沬之鄕矣로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="04b" n="3">이에 唐을 오 沬ᄉ 鄕애 놋다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="04b" n="4">云誰之思오 美孟姜矣로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="04b" n="4">누를 思뇨 美 孟姜이로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="04b-05a" n="5">期我乎桑中이며 要我乎上宮이오</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="04b-05a" n="5">나 桑中에 期며 나 上宮에 要고</sent><!--要^-->

<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="05a" n="1">送我乎淇之上矣로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="05a" n="1">나 淇ᄉ 上의셔 보내놋다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="05a" n="2">爰采麥矣 沬之北矣로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="05a" n="2">이에 麥을 오믈 沬ᄉ 北애 놋다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="05a" n="3">云誰之思오 美孟弋矣로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="05a" n="3">누 思뇨 美 孟弋이로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="05a" n="4">期我乎桑中이며 要我乎上宮이오</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="05a" n="4">나 桑中에 期며 나 上宮에 要고</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="05a" n="5">送我乎淇之上矣로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="05a" n="5">나 淇ᄉ 上의셔 보내놋다</sent>

<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="05b" n="1">爰采葑矣 沬之東矣로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="05b" n="1">이에 葑을 오믈 沬ᄉ 東애 놋다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="05b" n="2">云誰之思오 美孟庸矣로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="05b" n="2">누 思뇨 美 孟庸이로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="05b" n="3">期我乎桑中이며 要我乎上宮이오</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="05b" n="3">나 桑中에 期며 나 上宮에 要고</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="05b" n="4">送我乎淇之上矣로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="05b" n="4">나 淇ᄉ 上이셔 보내놋다</sent>
<sent type="title4" lang="chi" page="05b" n="5">桑中 三章</sent>

<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="06a" n="1">鶉之奔奔이며 鵲之疆疆이어</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="06a" n="1">鶉은 奔奔며 鵲은 彊彊거</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="06a" n="2">人之無良을 我以爲兄가</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="06a" n="2">사의 良티 아닌 이 내  兄을 삼안냐</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="06a" n="3">鵲之疆疆이며 鶉之奔奔이어</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="06a" n="3">鵲은 彊彊며 鶉은 奔奔거</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="06a" n="4">人之無良을 我以爲君가</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="06a" n="4">사의 良티 아닌 이 내  君을 삼안냐</sent>
<sent type="title4" lang="chi" page="06a" n="5">鶉之奔奔 二章</sent>

<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="06b" n="1">定之方中이어 作于楚宮니</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="06b" n="1">定이 뵈야호로 中커 楚ᄉ 宮을 作니</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="06b" n="2">揆之以日야 作于楚室이오</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="06b" n="2">揆호 日로  야 楚ᄉ 室을 作고</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="06b" n="3">樹之榛栗椅桐梓漆니</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="06b" n="3">榛과 栗과 椅과 桐과 梓과 漆을 시므니</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="06b" n="4">爰伐琴瑟이로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="06b" n="4">이예 伐야 琴과 瑟을 리로다</sent>

<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="07a" n="1">升彼虛矣야 以望楚矣로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="07a" n="1">뎌 虛의 올라  楚 望놋다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="07a" n="2">望楚與堂며 景山如京며</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="07a" n="2">楚과 다믓 堂을 望며 山과 다믓 京을 景며</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="07a" n="3">降觀于桑니</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="07a" n="3">降야 桑을 보니</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="07a" n="4">卜云其吉이러니</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="07a" n="4">卜애 닐오 그 吉타 더니</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="07a" n="5">終焉允臧이로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="07a" n="5">애 진실로 臧도다</sent>

<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="07b" n="1">靈雨旣零이어 命彼倌人야</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="07b" n="1">靈 雨ᅵ 이믜 零거 뎌 倌人을 命야</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="07b" n="2">星言夙駕야 說于桑田니</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="07b" n="2">星인 제 일 鴐야 桑田의 가 說니</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="07b" n="3">匪直也人의 秉心塞淵이라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="07b" n="3">갓 사의  秉홈이 塞고 淵 이 아니라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="07b" n="4">騋牝三千이로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="07b" n="4">鯠牝이 三千이로다</sent>
<sent type="title4" lang="chi" page="07b" n="5">定之方中 三章</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="07b" n="6">蝃蝀在東니 莫之敢指로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="07b" n="6">蝃蝀이 東에 이시니 敢히 指티 몯리로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="07b-08a" n="7">女子有行은 遠父母兄弟니라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="07b-08a" n="7">女子의 行을 둠은 父母와 兄弟 멀리 니라</sent><!--母^와-->

<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="08a" n="1">朝隮于西니 崇朝其雨ᅵ로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="08a" n="1">아 西의 隮니 朝ᅵ 崇 만 그 雨ᅵ로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="08a" n="2">女子有行은 遠兄弟父母ᅵ니라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="08a" n="2">女子의 行을 둠은 兄弟와 父母 멀리 니라</sent>

<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="08b" n="1">乃如之人也ᅵ여 懷昏姻也ᅵ로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="08b" n="1">이러  사이여 昏姻을 懷놋다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="08b" n="2">大無信也니 不知命也ᅵ로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="08b" n="2">키 信이 업스니 命을 아디 몯놋다</sent>
<sent type="title4" lang="chi" page="08b" n="3">蝃蝀 三章</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="08b" n="4">相鼠有皮니 人而無儀아</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="08b" n="4">鼠 相혼 皮이시니 사이오 儀 업스랴</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="08b" n="5">人而無儀 不死何爲오</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="08b" n="5">사이오 儀 업스니 죽디 아니코 므슴리오</sent>

<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="09a" n="1">相鼠有齒니 人而無止아</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="09a" n="1">鼠 相혼 齒 이시니 사이오 止 업스랴</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="09a" n="2">人而無止 不死何俟오</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="09a" n="2">사이오 止 업슨 이 죽디 아니코 므서슬 기이료</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="09a" n="3">相鼠有體니 人而無禮아</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="09a" n="3">鼠 相혼 體 이시니 사이오 禮 업스랴</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="09a" n="4">人而無禮 胡不遄死오</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="09a" n="4">사이오 禮 업슨 이 엇디 리 죽디 아닌뇨</sent>
